# FinWar local secrets for `wrangler dev`. Copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored).
#
# Optional bearer token guarding POST /simulate. When set, callers (FinOS) must
# send `Authorization: Bearer <FINWAR_TOKEN>`. Leave unset to run /simulate open.
# In production set it with: wrangler secret put FINWAR_TOKEN
FINWAR_TOKEN=
